93834.name: Northern Mockingbird
93834.text: I don't just immitate other birds. I'll gladly learn your ringtone too.

93840.name: Bobolink
93840.text: Overgown meadows are my favorite spot.

93847.name: Bachman's Sparrow
93847.text: Natural wildfires make my habitat so hospitable. Ironic, huh?

93873.name: Black Rail
93873.text: I like to spook tourists by running through the marsh making growling noises.

95058.name: Loggerhead Shrike
95058.text: Don't cross me. They don't call me the butcher bird for nothing.

104679.name: Bachman's Warbler
104679.text: Who doesn't like to holiday in Cuba?

104687.name: House Finch
104687.text: You must be mistaken, I'm too pretty to be invasive.

104688.name: Louisiana Waterthrush
104688.text: The ground hog knows nothing. My song descends at the true start of spring.

104697.name: Piping Plover
104697.text: Thanks for the work you've been doing. I have more plover friends every year.

104699.name: White-plumed Antbird
104699.text: I don't eat ants, they help me find food. I prefer their company to other birds frankly.

104707.name: Ascension Frigatebird
104707.text: I wish people would stop making fun of my red sac.

104713.name: Guam Kingfisher
104713.text: Maybe I don't get out much. I'm tired of getting into fights with tree snakes.

104714.name: Canada Warbler
104714.text: My 3,000 mile commute doesn't get me down at all. I have lots of audio books.

104715.name: Javan Hawk-eagle
104715.text: I am the rare Garuda, bow before this raptor.

104718.name: American Goldfinch
104718.text: I'm only gold when showing off. How else would you spot a tiny bird like me?

109277.name: Common Starling
109277.text: God, my kids are the worst.

109281.name: Sedge Wren
109281.text: People call me secretive. I much prefer discrete.

109283.name: Spix's Macaw
109283.text: They made a movie about me! I didn't see it.

143873.name: Stitchbird
143873.text: Don't kill 2 birds with one stone. Feed two birds with one scone!

143883.name: Red-headed Vulture
143883.text: I like to think I'm more mysterious than spooky.... No?

244778.name: Macaroni Penguin
244778.text: Do you think somewhere there's a pasta shapped like me?

279598.name: Rock Pigeon
279598.text: I may be just a rat with wings to you, but I know who I am.
